## Getting API Keys

### OpenWeatherMap API Key (Free)
1. Sign up at https://openweathermap.org/api
2. Go to API Keys section
3. Generate a new key
4. Add to WEATHER_API_KEY

### Gmail SMTP (for email)
1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Google account
2. Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
3. Generate an App Password
4. Use this password in SMTP_PASSWORD

---

## Production Notes

**⚠️ IMPORTANT for Production:**

1. Change ALL default passwords
2. Use strong, randomly generated JWT_SECRET (minimum 32 characters)
3. Use secure SMTP credentials
4. Store secrets in secure vault (Azure Key Vault, AWS Secrets Manager, etc.)
5. Never commit .env files to version control
6. Use different credentials for each environment (dev, staging, prod)
